{"tid":1650913,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣回應香港黑警移民消息","createTime":"2019-10-13T07:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T08:29:23.000Z","uid":239130,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2832548d641244f6deece6db380d0913e2414299","tid":1650913,"uid":239130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T07:34:02.000Z","msg":"【嚴格把關港澳居民移民來臺】<br />\n<br />\n有網路消息稱，香港&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑警</span></strong>&nbsp;將攜家眷大舉移民臺灣，並呼籲政府慎防！<br />\n<br />\n事實上，所有各類申請居留、定居案件，移民署都會透由各種管道進行安全查核，審視各項條件，將不法及犯罪阻絕於境外！<br />\n<br />\n根據現行香港澳門居民進入臺灣地區及居留定居許可辦法第16條規定，港澳居民因工作、投資、就學等相關事由，可申請在臺灣居留。<br />\n<br />\n但依同辦法第22條，如申請人有事實足認為有犯罪行為、有危害國家利益、公共安全、公共秩序，或從事恐怖活動之虞、參加或資助恐怖或暴力非法組織或其活動而隱瞞不報等情，移民署得不予許可其申請。<br />\n至於網路傳言600萬買房就可移民，這是錯誤訊息!香港澳門居民來台投資的項目，不包含單純購置不動產自用。因此，不得以購買600萬元以上的不動產置產事由，申請來台居留。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2891359300892454&amp;id=457582697603472\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2891359300892454%26id%3D457582697603472&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=489f8193\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2891359300892454&amp;id=457582697603472</a><br />\n香港黑警一齊嚟共享大灣區繁榮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好以為走到呀 你走都無得走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣助攻香港要繼續呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df66252087db2632e0db908b5d510beefd73f96d","tid":1650913,"uid":209543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T07:34:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dacf721f7bac0e344e241b98e0dba2599ca1d44d","tid":1650913,"uid":239130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T07:34:34.000Z","msg":"啱啱開錯台搵人同我推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5160a271ecda706b8f9efeec7744c03b96c0e414","tid":1650913,"uid":239130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T07:44:07.000Z","msg":"再推呀~~~~~~"},{"pid":"3680ef3fbfb954a01e6968440f3c417eb899d0df","tid":1650913,"uid":256620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"df66252087db2632e0db908b5d510beefd73f96d","tid":1650913,"uid":209543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T07:34:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T07:44:50.000Z","msg":"[即時] RTHK直播 TM 有打架康文署貨van有狗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1650940/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1650940/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"2de9db8889a7c58eef478c597792bd87b26c4f93","tid":1650913,"uid":239130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T08:08:31.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12385398af7f2baf97fad6ec9650d115bc7138ca","tid":1650913,"uid":239130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T08:25:59.000Z","msg":"pushhhhhhh"},{"pid":"98bfa7f8def91f69c3e4b6f1c3792d562318b10f","tid":1650913,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T08:29:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <ins> <div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 公民抗爭式交稅<br />\n<br />\n唔做正契弟<br />\n<br />\n愧對死去嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n＞【<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1637669】＜\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1637669】＜</a></div></ins></span></span>"},{"pid":"803332707d2d569916b287c237d83c540f5eb355","tid":1650913,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T08:29:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <ins> <div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 公民抗爭式交稅<br />\n<br />\n唔做正契弟<br />\n<br />\n愧對死去嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n＞【<a href=\"https://lih.kg/163